<t name="Offerings" t-name="website.judge_exciting">
    <t t-call="website.layout">
        <div id="wrap" class="oe_structure">
        <header style="padding:clamp(3.5rem,9vw,6.5rem) clamp(1.5rem,6vw,6rem) clamp(1.75rem,4vw,2.75rem);">
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:var(--text-label);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:var(--tracking-label);font-weight:var(--weight-medium);color:var(--vermilion);margin-bottom:20px;">
                <span style="color:var(--ink-faint);font-weight:var(--weight-regular);">03</span>
                <span>Offerings</span>
                <span style="flex:1;height:1px;background:var(--line);min-width:24px;"/>
            </div>
            <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:var(--weight-regular);text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink);font-size:clamp(2.75rem,8vw,6rem);line-height:var(--leading-tight);letter-spacing:-0.005em;margin:0;max-width:18ch;">I write tributes.</h1>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-style:italic;font-size:clamp(1.125rem,2.4vw,1.5rem);line-height:1.4;color:var(--ink-soft);margin:22px 0 0;max-width:40rem;">Eulogies, toasts, send-offs, keepsakes — the right words for the moments that matter, written for the people who have to stand up and say them.</p>
        </header>
        <section style="padding:clamp(4rem,10vw,7rem) clamp(1.5rem,6vw,6rem);border-top:1px solid var(--line);">
            <div style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;">
                <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(320px,1fr));gap:clamp(1rem,2vw,1.5rem);">
                <div style="background:var(--surface-card);border:none;border-top:2px solid var(--ink);border-radius:0;padding:var(--space-6);"><div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:12px;"><span style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:12px;color:var(--vermilion);">01</span><h3 style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:clamp(1.375rem,2.4vw,1.625rem);font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0.01em;line-height:1.15;margin:0;color:var(--ink);">Eulogies &amp; Memorials</h3></div><p style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:1.0625rem;line-height:1.6;color:var(--ink-soft);margin:14px 0 0;">The hardest one. You have a few days, a room full of people, and one chance to say who they were. Tell me the stories — I’ll find the through-line. Fast turnaround, handled gently.</p></div>
                <div style="background:var(--surface-card);border:none;border-top:2px solid var(--ink);border-radius:0;padding:var(--space-6);"><div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:12px;"><span style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:12px;color:var(--vermilion);">02</span><h3 style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:clamp(1.375rem,2.4vw,1.625rem);font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0.01em;line-height:1.15;margin:0;color:var(--ink);">Celebration Speeches</h3></div><p style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:1.0625rem;line-height:1.6;color:var(--ink-soft);margin:14px 0 0;">Weddings, anniversaries, milestone birthdays — the toast that sounds like you on your best day. Funny where it should be, sincere where it counts, short enough to keep the room.</p></div>
                <div style="background:var(--surface-card);border:none;border-top:2px solid var(--ink);border-radius:0;padding:var(--space-6);"><div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:12px;"><span style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:12px;color:var(--vermilion);">03</span><h3 style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:clamp(1.375rem,2.4vw,1.625rem);font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0.01em;line-height:1.15;margin:0;color:var(--ink);">Professional Tributes</h3></div><p style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:1.0625rem;line-height:1.6;color:var(--ink-soft);margin:14px 0 0;">Retirements, award introductions, colleague send-offs. Thirty years of work deserves more than a sheet cake and “good luck.” I turn a career into a story people actually want to hear.</p></div>
                <div style="background:var(--surface-card);border:none;border-top:2px solid var(--ink);border-radius:0;padding:var(--space-6);"><div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:12px;"><span style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:12px;color:var(--vermilion);">04</span><h3 style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:clamp(1.375rem,2.4vw,1.625rem);font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0.01em;line-height:1.15;margin:0;color:var(--ink);">Written Keepsakes</h3></div><p style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:1.0625rem;line-height:1.6;color:var(--ink-soft);margin:14px 0 0;">Not everything needs a podium. Letters for milestone moments, printed tribute pieces, memorials for pets who were family. Written to be handed over, folded up, and kept.</p></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section style="padding:clamp(4rem,10vw,7rem) clamp(1.5rem,6vw,6rem);border-top:1px solid var(--line);">
            <div style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;">
                <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:var(--text-label);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:var(--tracking-label);font-weight:var(--weight-medium);color:var(--text-accent);margin-bottom:28px;">
                    <span style="color:var(--ink-faint);font-weight:var(--weight-regular);">How it works</span>
                    <span style="flex:1;height:1px;background:var(--line);min-width:24px;"/>
                </div>
                <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:3rem 1fr;gap:18px;padding:26px 0;border-top:1px solid var(--line);align-items:baseline;"><span style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:1rem;color:var(--vermilion);">01</span><div><h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:var(--weight-regular);text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink);font-size:clamp(1.125rem,2vw,1.375rem);line-height:1.1;margin:0;">Book a consultation</h3><p style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:1.0625rem;line-height:1.6;color:var(--ink-soft);margin:10px 0 0;max-width:44rem;">Thirty minutes, $50, credited toward your final quote. You bring the occasion; I bring the questions.</p></div></div>
                <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:3rem 1fr;gap:18px;padding:26px 0;border-top:1px solid var(--line);align-items:baseline;"><span style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:1rem;color:var(--vermilion);">02</span><div><h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:var(--weight-regular);text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink);font-size:clamp(1.125rem,2vw,1.375rem);line-height:1.1;margin:0;">We talk</h3><p style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:1.0625rem;line-height:1.6;color:var(--ink-soft);margin:10px 0 0;max-width:44rem;">Who they are, the stories worth telling, and the things we absolutely will not mention. This conversation is the whole ballgame.</p></div></div>
                <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:3rem 1fr;gap:18px;padding:26px 0;border-top:1px solid var(--line);align-items:baseline;"><span style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:1rem;color:var(--vermilion);">03</span><div><h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:var(--weight-regular);text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink);font-size:clamp(1.125rem,2vw,1.375rem);line-height:1.1;margin:0;">You get a flat quote</h3><p style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:1.0625rem;line-height:1.6;color:var(--ink-soft);margin:10px 0 0;max-width:44rem;">One price for the piece, agreed up front. No meter running, no surprises on the invoice.</p></div></div>
                <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:3rem 1fr;gap:18px;padding:26px 0;border-top:1px solid var(--line);align-items:baseline;"><span style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:1rem;color:var(--vermilion);">04</span><div><h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:var(--weight-regular);text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink);font-size:clamp(1.125rem,2vw,1.375rem);line-height:1.1;margin:0;">I write, you react</h3><p style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:1.0625rem;line-height:1.6;color:var(--ink-soft);margin:10px 0 0;max-width:44rem;">A full draft, then one honest round of revisions until it sounds like you — not like a greeting card.</p></div></div>
                <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:3rem 1fr;gap:18px;padding:26px 0;border-top:1px solid var(--line);align-items:baseline;"><span style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:1rem;color:var(--vermilion);">05</span><div><h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:var(--weight-regular);text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink);font-size:clamp(1.125rem,2vw,1.375rem);line-height:1.1;margin:0;">It’s yours</h3><p style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:1.0625rem;line-height:1.6;color:var(--ink-soft);margin:10px 0 0;max-width:44rem;">Delivered ready to speak or print. Private by default, always.</p></div></div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section style="padding:clamp(3rem,7vw,5rem) clamp(1.5rem,6vw,6rem);border-top:1px solid var(--line);">
            <div style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;">
                <div style="border-left:2px solid var(--vermilion);padding-left:clamp(1.25rem,3vw,2rem);">
                    <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-style:italic;font-size:clamp(1.125rem,2.2vw,1.375rem);line-height:1.45;color:var(--ink);margin:0;max-width:46rem;">Everything you tell me stays between us. The samples on this site are real work with names and details changed — and nothing of yours gets published without your say-so.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section style="padding:clamp(4rem,10vw,7rem) clamp(1.5rem,6vw,6rem);border-top:1px solid var(--line);">
            <div style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;">
                <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:var(--weight-regular);text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink);font-size:clamp(2rem,5.5vw,3.75rem);line-height:var(--leading-tight);letter-spacing:-0.005em;margin:0;max-width:20ch;">Start with a conversation.</h2>
                <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:clamp(1.0625rem,2vw,1.25rem);line-height:1.6;color:var(--ink-soft);margin:18px 0 0;max-width:44rem;">Every tribute starts with a $50 consultation, credited toward your quote if we work together. Early customers: the first few are on me — ask.</p>
                <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center;gap:22px;margin-top:34px;">
                    <a href="/appointment" style="display:inline-block;background:var(--vermilion);color:var(--paper);font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:var(--text-label);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:var(--tracking-label);font-weight:var(--weight-medium);text-decoration:none;padding:16px 28px;border-radius:2px;">Book the consult →</a>
                    <a href="/blog" style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:var(--text-label);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:var(--tracking-label);font-weight:var(--weight-medium);color:var(--ink);text-decoration:none;border-bottom:1px solid var(--vermilion);padding-bottom:3px;">Or read a few tributes first</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <nav style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;gap:24px;padding:clamp(2rem,5vw,3rem) clamp(1.5rem,6vw,6rem);border-top:1px solid var(--line);">
            <div><a href="/home" style="display:inline-flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;text-decoration:none;align-items:flex-start;">
                <span style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:var(--text-meta);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:var(--tracking-label);color:var(--ink-faint);">Previous</span>
                <span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:baseline;gap:10px;font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:var(--weight-regular);text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink);font-size:clamp(1.375rem,3vw,2rem);line-height:1.0;letter-spacing:-0.005em;"><span style="color:var(--vermilion);">←</span><span>It’s on Random</span></span>
            </a></div>
            <div><a href="/blog" style="display:inline-flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;text-decoration:none;align-items:flex-end;">
                <span style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:var(--text-meta);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:var(--tracking-label);color:var(--ink-faint);">Next</span>
                <span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:baseline;gap:10px;font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:var(--weight-regular);text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink);font-size:clamp(1.375rem,3vw,2rem);line-height:1.0;letter-spacing:-0.005em;"><span>Entries</span><span style="color:var(--vermilion);">→</span></span>
            </a></div>
        </nav>
        </div>
    </t>
</t>
